# --- Dependencies ---
# Matches node_modules in root, /backend, and /frontend
**/node_modules/
**/jspm_packages/

# --- Environment Variables (CRITICAL) ---
# Never push your DB_PASSWORD or JWT_SECRET!
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.development.local
**/.env.test.local
**/.env.production.local

# --- Build & Output ---
**/dist/
**/build/
**/out/
**/.next/
**/.cache/

# --- TypeScript ---
# Ignore the build info but keep your source!
*.tsbuildinfo

# --- Logs ---
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/logs/
*.log

# --- IDE & OS ---
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj

# --- Testing ---
**/coverage/